{"tid":1545224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【Now新聞台】811被捕人脫骹及骨折需鑲金屬片及鏍絲","createTime":"2019-09-06T00:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T01:50:01.000Z","uid":37554,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e18bec7ef7a78bedda54b749118178d3cddf2426","tid":1545224,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:09:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361795&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=fffe07cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361795&h=bc52f683\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361795</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】在811衝突中，有六名被捕人士骨折，其中一名傷勢最嚴重的被捕人，左邊膊頭脫骹及骨折，需要鑲金屬片及鏍絲。他表示當日涉嫌非法集結被捕，暫未被落案起訴，計劃循法律途徑追究警方濫用暴力。<br />\n<br />\n已經成年的阿生，811當晚在銅鑼灣驅散行動中被捕。<br />\n<br />\n阿生說被警方按在地上後，沒有掙扎及反抗，亦沒有即時送院，而是被送到新屋嶺拘留中心，到凌晨三時許，即被捕後五小時，才被送到北區醫院急症室。<br />\n<br />\n經診斷他受襲擊，左邊閉合性肩關節前方脫位，閉合性肱骨近端四個部分都骨折，需要做緊急手術，鑲鈦金屬片及鏍絲固定。<br />\n<br />\n阿生現時每日要吃四次止痛藥，稍後會做物理治療，他說正與律師商討以法律途徑追究警方濫用暴力。<br />\n<br />\n曾經就類似情況協助巿民進行民事索償的律師表示，在審訊過程中，警方需向法庭披露使用武力及槍彈的守則，讓警方濫用暴力的爭議交由法庭裁決，但難以追究刑責。<br />\n<br />\n林洋鋐說，有些被捕人擔心有刑事案件在身，現階段進行民事索償，涉及披露案情可能對案件不利，未必會追究警方濫暴。"},{"pid":"5c1a6907923c1047f0a55f7fda4635955f247f19","tid":1545224,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:09:33.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1388ac270d3f02659c904c7c93ea0bb623a46fb","tid":1545224,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑狗"},{"pid":"f6f8a737a80efe1880094402a1e8408bc9a4242f","tid":1545224,"uid":169665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:11:07.000Z","msg":"沒有一隻黑警是無辜的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa030564dd6e002902fbb76a9ecf685caa473d0","tid":1545224,"uid":224882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:12:08.000Z","msg":"越打越多人行出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f8930d95780b88ec357a391869cad253f694b7","tid":1545224,"uid":258687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:12:15.000Z","msg":"前線同新屋嶺每隻狗都要被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6c8a80493332db45f920fd2ea95e1834cbd71d","tid":1545224,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"黑警冇一個無辜"},{"pid":"0ed73c8dc38518262158c61d31de8a6bf8fb8189","tid":1545224,"uid":26224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:24:41.000Z","msg":"黑警"},{"pid":"8e5c98fc3ece5fe6bc6aa7c5a29f1f9e0634a519","tid":1545224,"uid":110177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff60a005e6b1a179b6f08065f6b85505345f508","tid":1545224,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:39:57.000Z","msg":"差佬極醜惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bc7dde20d388bd317649cf29f6c9aad901c984","tid":1545224,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd933e22c82ab0d0b7de78eb01de1efb0b8fe18","tid":1545224,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n👉🏻<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>中英聯合聲明的謬誤</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n若果一件物件是從來未曾擁有過，拿到手上是談不上「恢復」及「收回」的。同樣道理，1997年前中華人民共和國從來未曾對香港行使過主權，如何談得上「恢復行使主權」？中華人民共和國的漢族（即「中國人民」）從來也沒有擁有過香港，試問又如何「收回」香港？<br />\n<br />\n因此，中華人民共和國取得香港的土地應該形容為「兼併」或「呑併」。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n👉🏻<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>不平等條約無效論是謊言</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如兩國以和平條約（Peace Treaty）終止戰爭，而某些領土由一國割讓予另一國，則在國際法中亦被視為透過割讓（Cession）而取得主權。過去的國際法觀點認為，以戰爭解決國與國之間的爭議屬國家的權利，而「和平條約」的作用是令交戰雙方以某些條款（包括部份領土的轉讓）為代價以終止戰爭。因此，按照「時空性原則」，1842年及1860年割讓香港島及九龍半島均符合當時的國際法。<br />\n<br />\n國際法中，領土的轉讓只有是否合法，而沒有平等不平等。<br />\n<br />\n在中華人民共和國成為國家之前，英國已經從清帝國手中符合國際法地取得香港的主權。另一方面，中華人民共和國亦從來沒有繼承過清帝國的仼何權益。因此，《中英聯合聲明》中所謂「對香港恢復行使主權」的「恢復」根本無從談起，並且只是一個猜想。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cbwr6sW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbwr6sW.png&h=7ee87500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPAHEN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx